AUXILIARY_DESCRIPTIONS.Alfredo Ortega-Chavez: Defendant and appellant convicted of conspiracy to bring or attempt to bring undocumented aliens into the United States, involved in smuggling operation with Ramon Gonzalez Sanchez and Alejandro Gonzalez Delgado
AUXILIARY_DESCRIPTIONS.GARWOOD: Circuit Judge presiding over the appeal of Alfredo Ortega-Chavez
AUXILIARY_DESCRIPTIONS.Ramon Gonzalez Sanchez: Co-conspirator, van driver, and participant in the smuggling operation with Ortega-Chavez and Alejandro Gonzalez Delgado, charged with attempting to bring illegal aliens into the United States
AUXILIARY_DESCRIPTIONS.Alejandro Gonzalez Delgado: Co-conspirator and participant in the smuggling operation with Ortega-Chavez and Ramon Gonzalez Sanchez, arrested for being an undocumented alien
